🍑 Vegan Pizza 📷 by @plumpeavegan 🚨🚨Recipe: 
Sauce:
1 jar of strained tomatoes (680 grams)
1 medium onion
3 garlic cloves
1 tbsp of maple syrup
2 tbsp of olive oil 
Salt & pepper
4 fresh basil leaves
Toppings:
Follow Your Heart mozzarella cheese 
1 zucchini 
1/2 a  ellow pepper
1/2 an onion
Mushrooms
1/2 a tomato
Fresh herbs
Directions:
-Sauté onions and garlic in olive oil until slightly golden. -Pour in strained tomatoes and once it comes to a boils, bring it down to a simmer on medium low heat.
-Add in the maple syrup and s&p. Simmer for 15 minutes and add in fresh basil. -Assemble pizza and bake at 450 for 10 minutes or depending on your doughs cook time! Enjoy! #thevegansclub 🍑
